Package com.opengamma.strata.market.option

Class MoneynessStrike

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.market.option.MoneynessStrike
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Strike, java.io.Serializable, org.joda.beans.Bean, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean
    public final class MoneynessStrike
extends java.lang.Object
implements Strike, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean, java.io.Serializable
    A strike based on moneyness.

    The moneyness is defined as strike/forward. The strike should be nonnegative and the forward should be strictly positive.
